description: Amendment to the approved application, reference PA/06/02068, permitted on 3rd October 2007 involving revised designs, layout and land uses, removing Office (B1) uses and providing 6 additional hotel rooms (143 in total), 195 serviced apartments, 54 additional residential units (1111 in total), additional retail floorspace, a health club and additional open space. (REGULATION 19 RESPONSE)  This application includes the submission of an Environmental Statement.
